{"tid":1226109,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《逃恥》編劇野木亞紀子談反送中： 香港人從此失去他們的香港","createTime":"2019-06-15T09:50:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T11:18:09.000Z","uid":130626,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f2cbf4c843165ed03ae732c78a447d6266dbc9ff","tid":1226109,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:50:45.000Z","msg":"炮製大熱劇《逃跑雖可恥但有用》的日本名編劇野木亞紀子，日前在Twitter分享以其筆名撰寫的千字文章「香港人の香港の話」，她在文中談到對香港的印象，又透露自己對《逃犯條例》修訂的看法等，野木亞紀子認為修例一旦通過，香港實行一國兩制的50年不變承諾恐怕會粉碎，香港人從此失去他們的香港。<br />\n野木亞紀子是近年日劇界數一數二的名編劇，先後創作《逃跑雖可恥但有用》、《無法成為野獸的我們》、《Unnatural》等多部作品，與新垣結衣屬最佳拍檔。野木亞紀子早在香港回歸前曾到港工作40天，她憶述97年主權移交前的留港經歷，她指當時香港的基建設施完善，電視技術及通訊也十分普及，是個先進城市。野木亞紀子自言一直沒想過要移居海外，當時卻有「如果是香港就可以留下生活」這個念頭，而她之後到過其他國家工作，最後也覺得只有香港能適合自己生活，對香港有不少情意結。<br />\n從回歸至今22年，野木亞紀子指可能會有人認為：「香港人的香港從來沒有存在」。不過屬於香港人的香港的確存在過，他們曾在當中生活過，也會有人說如果討厭的話可以離開吧。但是，香港人曾愛過的香港，就只有獨一無二的香港。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190615/large/1560578542_62e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190615%2Flarge%2F1560578542_62e0.jpg&h=675181ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190615/59718569\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190615%2F59718569&d=w67RnNhE2FzFZIT47vnPgKS5T01Y9%2BWuDWMC0%2BQyx7Y%3D&h=33061099\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190615%2F59718569&h=f7036226\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190615/59718569</a>"},{"pid":"d735feea533b65cfddacc6b2baecf4e6ec6299c8","tid":1226109,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:51:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>最終目標：推倒送中惡法。釋放義士。<br />\n<br />\n呢場仗我地仲未打贏，唔好掉以輕心。<br />\n<br />\n星期日出去遊行。<br />\n<br />\n星期一出去集會。<br />\n</strong></span></span></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b0033ac6344122d065192aa05b20e85c1c2f7c7e","tid":1226109,"uid":34383,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T09:52:37.000Z","msg":"結衣鼓勵香港人未"},{"pid":"6b3ebc150f16bf20c40f5fa0a758f39542212228","tid":1226109,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:12:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8f54739e53926db81d7ad78b49c742676c938285","tid":1226109,"uid":164591,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:16:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />hong Kong is not China, not yet."},{"pid":"bde20cde34d56c5e67dbe725a3e6c65f3dfb6033","tid":1226109,"uid":555,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:18:09.000Z","msg":"垃圾劇逃恥"}]}